headline: Does AbbVie's Latest AI Partnership Signal More Room for Its 2025 Rally?
summary: Thinking about whether to hold onto AbbVie stock, add more, or take some profits off the table? You're definitely not alone. AbbVie's been turning heads this year, with its share price notching a remarkable 28.3% gain since January and climbing 21.9% over the past 12 months. The momentum has been even more impressive over the long haul, up nearly 230% in five years. Those numbers suggest many investors are feeling more optimistic about AbbVie's growth potential or are reassessing the risks...
